<HEAD>Heritage USA Builder Asks Former Bakker Supporters to Help Buy Retreat</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ORLANDO, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The builder of Jim and Tammy Faye Bakker's
