spending package.
   ``The true measure of success isn't how many families we add to
housing assistance rolls. It's how many families move up and out _
and into the ranks of homeowners,'' Bush said Friday.
   He did not specify where he would find the money. The dollar
total was specified by aides.
</TEXT>
