<HEAD>Dollar Mixed, Gold Up</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: An AMer expected by 5:30 p.m. EST</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The U.S. dollar finished mixed Monday against
