<HEAD>Hershey Says It is Discussing Buying Ronzoni from General Foods</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HERSHEY, Pa. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Hershey Foods Corp. confirmed Monday it is
discussing buying Ronzoni Foods Corp. from General Foods, a unit of
Philip Morris Companies Inc.
   Hershey issued a statement that it and General Foods are
``working toward a definitive acquisition agreement.''
   The discussions include Ronzoni's dry pasta, sauces and cheese
businesses, which had 1988 sales of about $80 million.
